Deserialize a Raw Vector or String to an R Object

Source: R/rxRaw.R
rxDeserialize.Rd

Deserialize a Raw Vector or String to an R Object

Usage

rxDeserialize(x)

Arguments

x

raw vector or string to deserialize

Value

R object

Author

Matthew L. Fidler

Examples


rxDeserialize(rxSerialize(mtcars))
